DOMTextRun.characters: Your journey begins with a simple egg. We've kept it warm, and it's ready to hatch! From there begins the growing process. Feed your beast, play games and train it, and soon it will be ready to evolve! You can then participate in fierce battles to further grow your creature, and equip it with special items to help. Good luck, and take good care of it!
Daily towers give unique rewards rotated every day! Today's reward:

Towers contain traditional RPG battles where you can square off against other creature's, with each species possessing a unique moveset, allowing them to deal damage or change stats. But make sure to stay on your toes! Repeatedly using the same moves will cause them to stale, reducing the effect of all creature moves.

Every move has a Core. Physical moves do not stale as hard, but Magical moves typically do more damage. Move Types interact like the Arenas. Certain move types are more or less effective against creature types.
Feel free to continue playing! Your progress will be tracked.
Decrease the drill's time by 30 percent!

Arenas are areas where you can engage in fast-paced battles for several rounds at a time. Arenas are evolution and level locked, and have scaling difficulty. Battles work by having both creatures pick a "stance" where it then calculates a winner based on a system of advantages.

Battle stances are a rock-paper- scissors style system where every option has an weakness and a strength. Enemy creatures are more likely to use the stance based on their type, so you must observe and adapt accordingly.

Your creature is ready to hatch!
Your creature is ready to evolve!
Your creature can undergo rebirth to raise its stat and level caps! It will transform back into an egg and revert to level 1. LEVEL CAP - +10 STAT CAP - +20 percent"
Your egg has hatched into BLOB!

For years I rotted away in that body. What was once a bastion of glory, of love, of growth, when clutched for too long bleeds and distorts into greed, anger, hate. Life is not eternal. Please let go when the time is right. Moments do not last forever. THANK YOU FOR FREEING ME.
